Front Line is a military combat-themed arcade game that offers an exhilarating gaming experience. Available as a Chrome Extension and on the website retrobowls.org, this game allows players to immerse themselves in the intense world of warfare.

In Front Line, players assume the role of a skilled soldier on the front lines of a warzone. The game features fast-paced action, challenging missions, and realistic combat scenarios. Engage in thrilling gunfights, navigate dangerous environments, and complete various objectives to emerge victorious.
